        This template was created with <strong>@podcast-framework</strong>
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Next Steps:</h3>
      <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
        <li>Set up your Sanity CMS project</li>
        <li>Configure environment variables (copy .env.template to .env.local)</li>
        <li>Import your podcast episodes (from RSS or manually)</li>
        <li>Customize your theme and colors in Sanity</li>
        <li>Add your logo and branding</li>
